         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">4/2/87 ¶  ¶ Again I am obliged to you, noble Friend, for the list of names of several small consignments. ¶  On 15 November 1886 I sent off a considerable number of algae through the post that the spl...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">87.02.04a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Jacob Agardh</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Handskr. <seg style="">Avdl., Universitetsbibliotek, Lund, Sweden.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">4/2/87</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Wieder bin ich Ihnen dankbar verpflichtet, edler Freund, für die Namens Liste mehrerer kleiner Sendungen. Am 15 Nov. 1886 schickte ich durch die Post eine bedeutende Menge Algen ab, die mir </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">kurz zuvor</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> der prächtige Bracebr Wilson für Sie übersandte. Bei </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">mir</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> bleibt nichts liegen; Alles geht ab mit </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">erster</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> Post.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich mache weitere Versuche, Exemplare von Claudea Bennettiana in Frucht zu erlangen. Es soll mich innig freuen, wenn wir damit unserm unvergesslichen Freunde Sonder in der Algen Flora Australiens ein Ehren-Denkmal setzen können.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Für mehrere Druckschriften, namentlich Ihre letzte grosse Abhandlung, bin ich Ihnen vielleicht noch den Ausspruch meines Dankes schuldig. Ich freue mich, dass Sie auch gütig die Erwerbsquellen des Materials genannt, was ja meinem </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Departement</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> zu Gute kommt.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Wir arbeiten hier an Vorbereitungen zu einer antarct. Exped., was namentlich Hr. Baron Nordenskiold interessiren mag. Mein Antrag, dass Ballons zum Recognosciren benutzt werden sollen, ist angenommen. Hierbei mein Photogram für freundliche Entgegennahme. Haben Sie es schon, so bitte ich es einem andern Gelehrten zu geben.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Verehrungsvoll Ihr</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Ferd von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">4/2/87</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               </seg>Again I am obliged to you, noble Friend, for the list of names of several small consignments.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">J. Agardh to M, 25 December 1886 (in this edition as 86-12-25b).</p>
               </note> On 15 November 1886 I sent off a considerable number of algae through the post that the splendid Bracebridge Wilson sent me for you <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">shortly before</hi>
               </seg>.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See M to J. Agardh, 15 November 1886 (in this edition as <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>86-11-15a).</p>
               </note> Nothing remains at <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">my</hi>
               </seg> office; everything went off by the <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">first</hi>
               </seg> post.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am making further attempts to obtain specimens of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Claudea%20bennettiana">Claudea bennettiana</name>
               </seg> in fruit.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See M to E. Ramsay, 3 February 1887.</p>
               </note> It shall please me deeply if by so doing we can erect a monument to our unforgettable friend Sonder in the algal flora of Australia.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am still perhaps owing you the expression of my thanks for several papers, especially your last large paper.<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Probably Agardh (1873-90), part 4, issued in 1885. See the bibliographical comment in n. 2, T. Ware to M, 12 June 1874 (in this edition as 74-06-12a).</p>
                  <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
               </note> I am pleased that you also kindly named the sources of the material which is indeed of advantage to my <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">department</hi>
               </seg>.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>We are working here on preparations for an Antarctic expedition that may interest Baron Nordenskiold especially. My proposal that balloons should be used for reconnaissance is accepted. Enclosed my photograph for kindly acceptance. If you already have it, I ask that you give it to another savant.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Respectfully your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Claudea%20bennettiana">Claudea bennettiana</name>
            </p>
         </div>
